"{\"uid\": \"popcrush.com-tom-cruise-performs-jaw-dropping-stunt-paris-olympics-closing-ceremony\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Tom Cruiseabseiled down into the State de France during the closing ceremony at the Paris Olympics.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 99, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"TheMission: Impossiblestar performed one of his trademark stunts at Sunday's ceremony as he slid 115-feet down a rope from the venue's roof as part of the handover to Los Angeles for the 2028 Games.\", \"from\": 101, \"to\": 299, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 268, \"end\": 279, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\", \"score\": 0.9999999970095814, \"rank\": 2.1424363737808e-09, \"text\": \"Los Angeles\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Cruise\\u00a0was seen greeting athletes present at the ceremony before landing and taking the Olympic flag away on a motorbike.\", \"from\": 301, \"to\": 422, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"A pre-recorded segment then showed theTop Gunstar carrying the flag back to the US on a plane before he draped it over the Hollywood sign.\", \"from\": 424, \"to\": 562, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 547, \"end\": 561, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hollywood_Sign\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Hollywood sign\", \"types\": [\"Q41176\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hollywood_Sign\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hollywood_Sign\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"A report fromTMZearlier this month revealed that the Los Angeles element of the stunt was filmed in March and insiders admitted they had expected the Hollywood star to be spotted and the information to be leaked beforehand.\", \"from\": 564, \"to\": 787, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 617, \"end\": 628, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\", \"score\": 0.9999999970095814, \"rank\": 2.1424363737808e-09